Package com.example.eventscan.Entities

Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.example.eventscan.Entities.Event
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Event extends Object implements Serializable
The event class that holds all the necessary information for an event. Provides sufficient setters and getters for interfacing with the class. If you change this don't forget to change Database/EventDatabaseRepresentation
